1583
01:48:20,407 --> 01:48:23,118
...this disgrace to the cause of justice.

1584
01:48:24,536 --> 01:48:26,372
I wish you Godspeed.

1585
01:48:28,625 --> 01:48:30,168
Case dismissed.

1586
