that he was taking bribes.

1601
01:49:40,419 --> 01:49:42,547
That Carolyn was the courier.

1602
01:49:45,383 --> 01:49:47,218
You blackmailed him, Sandy.

1603
01:49:52,225 --> 01:49:53,893
