1684
01:59:00,089 --> 01:59:02,091
Another break-in by some...

1685
01:59:02,634 --> 01:59:04,303
...sex-crazed man.

1686
01:59:09,433 --> 01:59:10,977
But all his life...

1687
01:59:12,605 --> 01:59:14,732
...he'll know that it was her.

1688
01:59:19,697 --> 01:59:22,575
