...some time before, a housewarming gift
from her husband and his office.

1690
01:59:27,790 --> 01:59:29,583
She buys another set.

1691
01:59:30,918 --> 01:59:33,505
Her husband has a beer one night...

1692
01:59:35,799 --> 01:59:38,135
