1705
02:00:35,830 --> 02:00:37,748
The destroyer is destroyed.

1706
02:00:41,378 --> 02:00:43,380
She takes a cord out...

1707
02:00:45,382 --> 02:00:47,426
...that she brought along...

1708
02:00:49,637 --> 02:00:51,431
